		<skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">A sea within a sea, the Andaman Sea consists of that part of the Indian Ocean bordered by Myanmar, Thailand, Malaysia, Sumatra and the Andaman and Nicobar Islands.</skos:scopeNote>
